summary: This is an email chain from May 28, 2021, regarding the coordination of receiving a new file from the FBI for the Maxwell case via the USAfx system. The sender requests a team member to handle the upload, and a reply indicates the task will be completed the following Monday.

persons.name: Maxwell
persons.context: The email chain is about receiving a new file for the Maxwell case from the FBI.

events.title: Coordination for Maxwell case file transfer
events.description: An email is sent to coordinate receiving a new file from the FBI for the Maxwell case via USAfx.

keyFacts: The FBI had a new file pertaining to the Maxwell case as of May 28, 2021.
The file transfer was to be coordinated via the USAfx system.
The email indicates ongoing legal proceedings or evidence handling in the Maxwell case at that time.
